{"id":"50fa7315-a14f-46f0-87d5-7b60373e6a56","name":"Spider-Verse","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">🕸️🕷️🕸️</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Spider-Man, Miles Morales, Spider-Man 2099, Night-Spider, Silk, Ghost-Spider, Superior Spider-Man, Spider-Ham, Spider-Man Noir, Jessica Drew, Ben Reilly, ect.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>The Spider-Verse is a sprawling, multiverse that brings together various versions of Spider-Man from alternate realities. Peter Parker (the original Spider-Man) teams up with numerous other Spider-People, including Miles Morales, Spider-Gwen, Spider-Man 2099, Silk, and even alternate versions like Spider-Man Noir and Spider-Ham. Together, they must protect their worlds from danger while navigating the complexities of the Web of Life and Destiny, which connects all Spider-beings.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/53f26d0e-cf8a-4e90-8e79-ff649e51f58e_a08df67a-1a53-49cf-9fb4-a1b26730c9e2.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/53f26d0e-cf8a-4e90-8e79-ff649e51f58e_5f8cc157-15ab-418c-bf4e-74ebd6df1a57.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/53f26d0e-cf8a-4e90-8e79-ff649e51f58e_86b3515f-4c07-4327-a7c3-4072532f7205.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/53f26d0e-cf8a-4e90-8e79-ff649e51f58e_7f508512-5368-4dda-8451-8e9854af24fd.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/53f26d0e-cf8a-4e90-8e79-ff649e51f58e_cb73fc31-c16d-4058-b3ce-b13037fe7ac6.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"wi